Where to Watch

Actor-comic Eddie Griffin's star continues to rise as he brings the house down in this hilarious stand-up comedy performance from Chicago. The film also includes scenes with his family in his home town of Kansas City, Mo., where Griffin recalls his childhood with his mother and two uncles. George Gallo directed.
